name: Private First Class Jesse Givens
comments: Recorded live at the group's tenth anniversary concert in the Twin Cities, Minnesota. The lyrics were taken from a letter written by Private Jesse Givens of Springfield, Missouri. Givens was killed in Iraq on May 1, 2003 when his tank crashed into the Euphrates River. Less than two weeks earlier he had written a heartfelt letter to his pregnant wife.
